      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/ortho-def-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "最后连接垂心与三个顶点，取这三条线段的中点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "ortho",
      "line_id": "def-6",
      "filename": "ortho-def-6.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nine-point-circle/ortho-def-6.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "三个中点、三个垂足、三个边中点，一共正好九个点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nine-point-circle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
